      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite covering hemolysis model components; formal regression testing at each release.",
      "rationale": "Solver is version controlled and a partial test suite exists, but regression testing does not cover the hemolysis damage model specifically. Achieved level 2 against required level 4 at MRL 5."
    },
    {
