      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions fully characterized with measured boundary conditions traceable to VAD operating envelope; fluid rheology matched to blood analog.",
      "rationale": "Experimental flow rates and speeds are documented; however, inlet turbulence intensity and fluid temperature were not measured and were assumed from literature values, reducing fidelity of boundary condition matching."
