      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g., E_rel or U95) applied to hemolysis index predictions versus measurements; statistical comparison across all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative agreement reported; no formal quantitative comparison metric applied to hemolysis index predictions. Visual overlay of predicted vs measured values provided without uncertainty bands."
