      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation (normalized index of hemolysis) are directly equivalent to QoIs required for regulatory decision (absolute hemolysis index).",
      "rationale": "Validation QoI is normalized index of hemolysis (NIH); regulatory decision requires absolute hemolysis index (HI). Conversion factor applied but introduces additional uncertainty not fully propagated."
    },
