      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities performed on geometry and operating conditions within the VAD COU envelope; no significant extrapolation from validation domain to COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump geometry at overlapping but not identical operating conditions. VAD COU includes pulsatile flow conditions not represented in the steady-state validation dataset."
    },
