      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical characterization of blood analog fluid properties across multiple sample batches; inter-batch variability quantified and propagated.",
      "rationale": "Test sample variability was not assessed. A single batch of blood analog was used for all experiments; inter-batch variability in viscosity and density was not characterized. Flagged as epistemic gap."
    },
