      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal mapping between experimental input parameters and simulation boundary conditions; equivalency demonstrated via dimensional analysis or direct measurement comparison.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters was not formally assessed. Boundary conditions were set to nominal experimental values without systematic verification of equivalency between physical and computational domains. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    }
